social_posts.post_text: It’s about that time! I’ll be gearing up next week to hit the ice over my winter break! Who’s with me? I’ll have @fishseaguar IceX in hand!

Winter Smallmouth Fishing on the #upppermississippiriver on this beauty 40degree day in Minnesota! #winterfishing #openwater #fishingvideo #riverfishing #video #womenwhofish #momswhofish #minnesotafishing @fishseaguar

That Mississippi Gold ! This is what you call a #walleye ! This beauty was caught in 20-22ft deep on a Dubuque Rig with 20lb @fishseaguar smack down braid to a 3 way swivel with a 18inch 12lb tatsu flouro carbon leader with a weightless 1/0 strait shank Aberdeen hook and firecracker moxie trailer. And the bottom was a 10inch leader with a 5/8 gold jig head with chartreuse pulse R.

All for Gods Glory not ours. The sooner you figure that out in our sport the happier and at peace you will be. The things of this world mean nothing. Live for the ✝️ and doing good for others . That’s my truth. #nicolefishing

#throwbackthursday This time of year gets emotional for me. Coming up on 11 year to the man I lost to cancer #mutiplemyeloma who inspired my entire fishing career. It was and still is all for your and Gods glory Dad. Love forever, love you for always, as long as I’m living my daddy you will be. #nicolefishing #daddysgirl #thisissuccess #allforgodsglory #jesuscan 🤲🏽✝️🎣💕👨‍👧
This is sobriety!! Gopher state here I come!5k of MN sober communities coming together to celebrate sobriety is something special ! #soberliving #soberissexy #nicolefishing

This was one of the most magical weekends I have ever had. To see 4k-5k addicts and alcoholics come together as family and to fellwoship was utterly amazing. I had tremendous growth and humility this weekend. I was the event lead for our west end suite and could not have been happier with how things turned out. 

Sobriety singled handedly has been the biggest blessed in my life to rid the trauma and fears I never delt with after losing my father to cancer young and going through an abusive marriage and abusiing myself in past. That has stopped .  The self hating and self seeking ego, pride driving, attention seeking, broken soul.  Stopped My Will and All Gods. I am renewed. All in becasue this programs works of AA and God. 

I had one more area I needed to let go and truly surrender that area these past few  days but admitting  I was powerless, that God can fix it  and surrendering it to Him . Thank you Jesus for loving me and all you amazing people in Recovery !! I love you all! In the “Sunlight of the Spirit … I am Free baby!! I am free. “ #soberissexy #soberaf ##nicolefishing #soberliving #renewed #wedorecover #thisissobriety #onldlifegone ✝️☮️💜
#motivationalmonday My sober verse . Power, Love , Sound Mind! #nicolefishing

7th or 8th year fishing the @mntc_hope fishing challenge! Super special derby for me being in recovery myself. Trying for a win tomorrow but it’s never about that and all about the men and women in the program of recovery at #mntc ! #wedprecocer #soberlofe #soberissexy #godglory

We fished our hearts out today and caught them good ! All for Gods glory and recovery ! What an amazing day. Truly we did my two favorite things all day… worshiped and fished on one of my favorite lakes Gull. We had 12.89lbs for 3 bass and rocky for 3rd place. We were leading it then these amazing high school girls came in crushing  it with over 13lbs!! I got teary eyes because the  next generation of women coming up in our sport is bright! It was amazing to see them win the bass division and win my guide trip! What a blessing. 

This derby always hits different now that I am 2.8 years sober. If you are someone you know is suffering from addiction there is help at Mn Adult & Teen Challenge . God loves you all and you can recover! 2 Timothy 1:7 Thank you Lord! #myheartisfull 💜🤲🏽🎣✝️ #mntc #gulllake @mntc_hope

11 years ago on this day since you been gone Dad. God knew you were one of the good ones and took you at just 55 years old. From @multiplemyeloma.awareness cancer.
. But boy did he have bigger plans in store for your daughters after your death.. 
An angler to fish all over the country for @walmart and to spread gods word, A musician to spread and learn her own talents just like yours @indigo_onyxx and to make her own music. She  gets royalties on it and opened for waca waca flame. Lastly,  @banana2029 a go getter , passionate and highly successful CPG executive with clients like PlayStation! Wow did you raise us right and oh how God has blessed us. You would be proud. And you would be so proud of your grandson @colecampbell2418  who shares your birthday and is super smart at school and an amazing snowboarder! 
I’m not sad on this.. no more. God promises us that we will all be together again in His kingdom in heaven! I love you and miss you! Catch some crappies for me while you wait! #daddysgirl #iloveyoudaddy #nicolefishing

#motivationalmonday I have never been more spiritually fit than I am right now. I am humble and graceful with myself becasue of Christ’s love for me through sobriety. I can set boundaries now and hold them. I never had them before in my using days because I truly hated myself. 

When we continue to let the Lord in…He will mends all parts of your heart and life leaving you unbothered and unharmed by actions of others because you are so armed with Gods light and protection. He restores and brings peace, love , Serenity and joy to your life. Galatians 5:22-23 
What are you holding on to that destroying your peace? I pray all of you find Him now and surrender. #nicolefishing #faith #christianquotes 2 Timothy 1:7✝️💜🎣

#transformtuesday Sharing Gods truth about sobriety. Super special weekend. So much gratitude and love in my heart. That’s why I do what I do to protect it and let God be God. 

He knows his plans for me.. Jerimiah 29:11 . Hard sometimes to trust but I know he’s got something, someone and more waiting for me . I earned it and deserve it in His name not mine. 💜✝️🎣

The love of catching bass will never fade .. my heart in this for the better . To bring a new element of fishing to the sobriety world. I can’t wait what God has in store #greatfulheart #allforhisglory #nicolefishing ✝️💜🎣
Whatever your going through… ain’t no problem for God. Gods got it. Lean into some fish this weekend! #nicolefishing

To all my people in recovery, I’ve been thinking about you over the holiday weekend. I love you. Holidays can bring up lots of emotions for us in recovery. Today I felt a lot of those whirlwind of emotions from grief to happiness. The past memories of fishing with my father on these days and the not so pretty past of getting wasted on big island reminded me of how hard I’ve worked and how far I’ve come. 

I took a lot of time alone to reflect for how incredible grateful Iam for the beautiful sober life God has given me. The serenity , the friends that love me for the real me and everything in between. Sobriety isn’t always pretty but dang… it’s been the biggest gift and blessing in my life. Thank you Lord. 🎇🎣 #sober #soberlife #soberholidays #nicolefishing 💜

Please check on your loved ones

Super excited to announce my next big chapter in my fishing career.. I have started a nonprofit called #reelcovery , in which our mission is to “ Empower and Inspire Addiction Recovery Through Fishing and Outreach.” We want to get people to  unhook addiction and hook fishing 🎣💜. I’m currently building a team and business plan to launch. We need investors and partners who want to see this 501c succeed. Let’s use the restorative nature of fishing in the recovery world and change lives. Who’s with me? Follow us @reelcovery_  #2Timothy1:7 #nicolefishing #nonprofitsofinstagram

I’ll tell you 40 and sober feels good. Actually dealing with past trauma hasn’t been easy. A lot has come out this past year. But you stand tall, we follow God, we had set backs , but comebacks and we rise up. Super excited for @reelcovery_  and who’s going to show up for me fully. Thank you Lord for loving me. #2timothy1:7 #nicolefishing✝️🎣 #sobriety #thisis40 #godglow

@wefestmn Ready!! Who’s coming? I’m working as event manager at the Ranch house on the hill. Come say hi! And if any of my sober people want to fellowship in the am before I work DM me! I’ll be hitting up meetings and worshiping ✝️💜🤲🏽 before! Let’s roll! #countrymusic #wefest #wefestmn #wefest2023

That’s a wrap @wefestmn ! This was a transformative week for me. I did a lot of necessary healing. Sobriety intact and reiterated why I’m doing what I’m doing. God showed up exactly when I needed him through the amazing people I worked with and met. HE NEVER FAILS US! We just have to stay obedient ! My heart is so happy and full. I needed this week away to grind and work with these amazing people, be in a leadership role and do what I do best and use my skill sets to honor God. Time to get @reelcovery_ rolling. Thank you Lord for trusting me and thank you to the wonderful people of WeFest especially the Hopela family and all the amazing bartenders for trusting me to lead the hill.. migraines and all.. I love you all! #nicolefishing #eventmanagement #country #countrymusic

This picture popped up on my timeline….our first national appearance fishing for Walmart down on Lake Toho. I’m humbled by this photo and have so much gratitude. Our entire career leading up to today was in Gods light and honor after so much grief in losing my father. We have accomplished a decade of some pretty cool stuff…. and didn’t come with struggles and trials. But this photo is a reminder why we started, what’s the purpose ✝️ and where God is leading with @reelcovery_ . Nothing absolutely nothing is of my doing and is all for Gods glory and the support of my sponsors , family, fans, friends old and new. We ride together for one purpose alone! Jesus. #nicolefishing
